---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Hand Tools Factory China | About WOOKTOOL"
  description="Learn about WOOKTOOL, a China hand tools factory offering tape measure manufacturing, OEM/ODM customization, quality control, and export service."
  path="/about/"
>
  <section class="page-intro"><div><p class="eyebrow">About us</p><h1>Hand Tools Factory in China</h1><p>WOOKTOOL supports B2B buyers with custom tape measures, utility knives, screwdriver sets, and OEM/ODM hand tools made for importer, distributor, and private-label programs.</p></div></section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner grid two">
      <div>
        <h2>Export-oriented manufacturing support</h2>
        <p>Our work is built around practical factory coordination, clear product details, and reliable communication. Buyers can use WOOKTOOL as a direct sourcing partner for standard hand tools and customized product programs.</p>
        <p>The website uses placeholder images and contact details so your team can replace them later with real factory photos, certificates, catalogs, and sales contacts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid two">
        <article class="info-card"><h3>Manufacturing experience</h3><p>Product support for tape measures, utility knives, screwdriver sets, and related hand tool categories.</p></article>
        <article class="info-card"><h3>Self-operated export team</h3><p>Inquiry handling, quotation preparation, sample follow-up, and order communication for overseas buyers.</p></article>
        <article class="info-card"><h3>Quality control</h3><p>Inspection checkpoints can be defined for raw materials, production, finished products, packaging, and shipment.</p></article>
        <article class="info-card"><h3>Service capability</h3><p>OEM branding, packaging development, flexible MOQ discussion, and support for global market buyers.</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <CTA title="Need a China hand tools factory for your brand?" />
</BaseLayout>
